@page "/checklist"
@rendermode InteractiveServer

<PageTitle>Counter</PageTitle>

<h1>Website Checklist</h1>

<RadzenRow>
	<RadzenColumn>
		<article>
			<h2>1. General Structure</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>&#x2714; Minimum of 3-5 interconnected pages</li>
				<li>&#x2714; Use of a clear navigation system</li>
			</ul>
		</article>

		<article>
			<h2>2. HTML</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>&#x2714; Correct use of semantic tags</li>
				<li>
					Includes:
					<ul>
						<li>&#x2714; Tables</li>
						<li>&#x2714; DropDowns</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</article>

		<article>
			<h2>3. CSS</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>&#x2714; Separation of styles and structure</li>
				<li>
					Attractive design using:
					<ul>
						<li>&#x2714; Advanced selectors</li>
						<li>&#x2714; Styles for hover, focus, active states</li>
						<li>&#x2714; Consistent colors and fonts</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</article>

		<article>
			<h2>4. JavaScript</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Adding interactivity with minimum 2-3 functionalities:</li>
				<li>&#x2714; Dynamic change of background</li>
				<li>&#x2714; Image gallery or slider</li>
				<li>&#x2714; Separation of JavaScript code into external files</li>
			</ul>
		</article>

		<article>
			<h2>5. Connection with an External API</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>&#x2714; Example: Displaying weather from a weather API</li>
			</ul>
		</article>
	</RadzenColumn>
	<RadzenColumn>
		<article>
			<h2>6. Optimization</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>&#x2714; Reasonable loading time</li>
				<li>&#x2714; Optimized images for the web</li>
				<li>&#x2714; Correct use of CSS and JS files (minimization, if possible)</li>
			</ul>
		</article>

		<article>
			<h2>7. Additional Criteria</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>&#x2714; Use of a CSS framework (Radzen/Bootstrap)</li>
				<li>&#x2714; Introduction of a simple front-end framework (Blazor)</li>
				<li>&#x2714; Configuration and use of GitHub for versioning and deployment</li>
			</ul>
		</article>

		<article>
			<h2>8. Documentation</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>
					A README.md file that includes:
					<ul>
						<li>&#x2714; Purpose of the site</li>
						<li>&#x2714; Installation/running instructions</li>
						<li>&#x2714; References used</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</article>

		<article>
			<h2>9. Testing</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>&#x2714; Testing on different browsers</li>
				<li>&#x2714; Ensuring the site works without errors in the browser console</li>
			</ul>
		</article>
	</RadzenColumn>

</RadzenRow>
